title: The Recruit - S02E10
description:
The Recruit - S02E10

Former AFL player and Coach, Mick Malthouse, joined by former Hawthorn champion and Fox Footy commentator Ben Dixon, Port Adelaide's world class fitness guru Darren Burgess, and accomplished sports administrator Leigh Russell have seen 15 Recruits from across the country put through their paces. Now the final three Recruits face the Judges and 18 AFL Reps at the Melbourne Crown, where Ryan 'Fitzy' Fitzgerald hosts the draft to announce the winner of an AFL club contract.
